metadata.name: being
metadata.description:
who are we and why did we come here? 

where do we as individuals begin and end? 

what defines us as existing? 


these are questions with many answers but no absolute truth, feel free to share with me what your answers would be and i will share mine back. 


- a film photography shot with my canon f1 and portra 400.


9.6084° N, 85.1350° W
